@startuml Sequence_ViewAndFilter
title Sequence Diagram - Xem danh sách & Lọc công việc

actor "Người dùng" as User
participant "HomePage\n(Component)" as Home
participant "StatsAndFilters" as Filters
participant "DatetimeFilter" as DateFilter
participant "Axios" as Axios
participant "authMiddleware" as MW
participant "GET /api/tasks\n(Backend)" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB

== Khi trang HomePage mount ==

Home -> Home : useEffect([dateQuery])\n→ fetchTasks()
activate Home

Home -> Axios : GET /tasks?filter=today
activate Axios
Axios -> MW : HTTP GET (Bearer token)
activate MW
MW -> API : next()
deactivate MW
activate API

API -> API : Xác định startDate\ntừ query param "filter"
note right of API
  switch(filter):
    'today' → đầu ngày hôm nay
    'week'  → thứ Hai tuần này
    'month' → ngày 1 tháng này
    'all'   → null (không lọc)
end note

API -> API : query = {userId}\nnếu startDate: query.createdAt = {$gte: startDate}

API -> DB : Task.aggregate([\n  {$match: query},\n  {$facet: {\n    tasks: [{$sort: {createdAt: -1}}],\n    activeTaskCount: [...],\n    completedTaskCount: [...]\n  }}\n])
activate DB
DB --> API : result
deactivate DB

API --> Axios : 200 {tasks,\nactiveTaskCount,\ncompletedTaskCount}
deactivate API
Axios --> Home : response.data
deactivate Axios

Home -> Home : setTaskBuffer(tasks)\nsetActiveTaskCount(...)\nsetCompletedTaskCount(...)

== Người dùng lọc theo trạng thái ==

User -> Filters : Click "Đang Thực Hiện"
activate Filters
Filters -> Home : setFilter('active')
deactivate Filters

Home -> Home : filteredTasks = taskBuffer\n.filter(t => t.status === 'active')
Home -> Home : visibleTasks = filteredTasks\n.slice(start, end)
Home -> Home : setPage(1)

== Người dùng lọc theo thời gian ==

User -> DateFilter : Chọn "Tuần này"
activate DateFilter
DateFilter -> Home : setDateQuery('week')
deactivate DateFilter

Home -> Home : useEffect trigger\n→ fetchTasks() với filter=week
Home -> Axios : GET /tasks?filter=week
note right: Luồng tương tự như trên

deactivate Home
@enduml
